snippet.title: Angra - Reaching Horizons (Cover by SIEG ft. Leo Patkovic)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial
Leo Patkovic YouTube : https://www.youtube.com/user/leogitara/

I started a long journey to fly to the sky, but all the nostalgic faces that rise over the horizon are still there... so I'm sending my soul into each wave, then I hope they return to reach my land.

Leo is not very well known, but he is very sensual and a great guitarist. Please visit Leo's channel.

Angra - Reaching Horizons (Cover by SIEG ft. Leo Patkovic)

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Vocals, Mixing, Mastering and Video Editing
Leo Patkovic (Leo Patkovic, Serbia) - Guitars
